titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: MORE THAN THREE RECTAL WASHOUTS RECEIVED INDICATOR - Description

div.p: MORE THAN THREE RECTAL WASHOUTS RECEIVED INDICATOR is the same as attribute MORE THAN THREE RECTAL WASHOUTS RECEIVED INDICATOR.

For the National Neonatal Data Set - Episodic and Daily Care, MORE THAN THREE RECTAL WASHOUTS RECEIVED INDICATOR indicates whether the baby had more than three rectal washouts on the NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE.
